    "title": "Pakistan interior minister arrives in Iran",
    "description": "TEHRAN: Pakistan’s interior minister arrived in Iran on Saturday after planned talks between Iran and the US in Switzerland were postponed, Iranian media reported. Tehran and Washington were due to hold talks in Switzerland on Friday, after signing a memorandum of understanding ending the war in the Middle East, but the latest negotiations have been postponed until Sunday.",
